snippet.title: Prized Pooky
snippet.description: Mr. Allwork offers to buy Pooky from Jon and Garfield. Watch more of The Garfield Show on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: By the Power of Friendship
snippet.description: Gumball buys a little girl's tricycle and races across town to get his best friend back. Watch more of The Amazing World of Gumball on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Silence Is Golden
snippet.description: Blue Falcon, Wonder Woman, Birdman, Zan, and Zandor combine their powers and their cash to buy popcorn at the movies. Watch more Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Sleep Disorder/Tom's In-Tents Adventure
snippet.description: Sleep Disorder: Rick buys Ginger a brand new mattress with a lot of high tech features. Tom is under strict orders to never sleep on it! Tom's In-Tents Adventure: Tom and Jerry get a taste of the great outdoors on their camping trip to Yosemite.

snippet.title: Coyote Chase
snippet.description: Help Wile E. Coyote build the perfect rocket to catch the Road Runner in this 3D racing game.

snippet.title: Jumping Finn
snippet.description: Launch, bounce and fling Finn all the way to the Ice Kingdom.
